      Constructor and Description
      Halfsegment(PointIF p0, PointIF p1, boolean leftDominating)
      Constructor to create a 'Halfsegment' object by passing the endpoints and a flag which indicate the dominating point of this segment
      The passed points will be assigned to the internal leftPoint and rightPoint by the following rule:
      leftPoint = min(p0, p1)
      rightPoint = max(p0, p1)
      Segment(PointIF p0, PointIF p1)
      Constructor for an 'Segment' object
      The passed points will be assigned to the internal leftPoint and rightPoint by the following rule:

      rightPoint = max(p0, p1)
